1
00:00:00,480 --> 00:00:05,056
=Lost You Forever S1=

2
00:00:05,056 --> 00:00:07,296
(Lost You Forever S1 Special Edition 6)

3
00:00:07,424 --> 00:00:08,640
(Cheng'en Palace)

4
00:00:08,640 --> 00:00:09,560
We've arrived.

5
00:00:12,600 --> 00:00:13,720
Wen Xiaoliu was trying

6
00:00:13,720 --> 00:00:14,520
to escape,

7
00:00:14,520 --> 00:00:15,600
so I slightly punished him.

8
00:00:15,880 --> 00:00:17,040
Stay for a meal together.

9
00:00:19,360 --> 00:00:20,559
I'm a countryman.

10
00:00:20,639 --> 00:00:22,239
It's my first time
seeing so much delicious food.

11
00:00:22,239 --> 00:00:22,959
Please forgive me

12
00:00:23,360 --> 00:00:24,760
if I behave improperly.

13
00:00:25,360 --> 00:00:27,239
I've already asked the chef
to prepare Qingai Cake.

14
00:00:27,239 --> 00:00:30,040
You can eat some
while listening to a story before bed.

15
00:00:30,680 --> 00:00:31,719
I want to eat it

16
00:00:31,719 --> 00:00:32,720
while my mother

17
00:00:32,720 --> 00:00:33,639
tells me a story.

18
00:00:34,560 --> 00:00:35,200
Master.

19
00:00:36,159 --> 00:00:37,119
She's Xiaoyao?

20
00:00:43,360 --> 00:00:46,080
(In fact, you've already
told me who you are.)

21
00:00:47,599 --> 00:00:50,000
(But I was blinded by cruelty)

22
00:00:50,919 --> 00:00:52,680
(and failed to notice it.)

23
00:00:52,794 --> 00:00:57,824
♪For forever accompanying you♪

24
00:00:58,240 --> 00:01:04,032
♪Let momentary sorrow and joy fly♪

25
00:01:06,160 --> 00:01:07,239
(Break his leg.)

26
00:01:08,352 --> 00:01:08,992
Xuan.

27
00:01:09,919 --> 00:01:10,720
Does it hurt?

28
00:01:12,559 --> 00:01:13,639
Take good care of him.

29
00:01:14,360 --> 00:01:16,279
(If I had kept my promise)

30
00:01:16,599 --> 00:01:18,319
(to pick Xiaoyao up in Mount Jade,)

31
00:01:18,319 --> 00:01:20,199
(Xiaoyao wouldn't have been lost.)

32
00:01:21,839 --> 00:01:22,639
Xiaoyao.

33
00:01:23,319 --> 00:01:24,800
I'm going back to Zhaoyun Peak.

34
00:01:25,160 --> 00:01:27,919
You have to go back, anyway.

35
00:01:28,160 --> 00:01:29,680
No matter how hard the journey is,

36
00:01:30,599 --> 00:01:33,680
I'm no longer embarking on it alone.

37
00:01:35,839 --> 00:01:37,519
I decided to be the Princess of Haoling.

38
00:01:37,720 --> 00:01:38,599
Are you doing it for me?

39
00:01:38,879 --> 00:01:40,800
Not entirely.

40
00:01:40,800 --> 00:01:41,760
Because I think

41
00:01:41,760 --> 00:01:44,199
being a princess is not completely bad.

42
00:01:45,800 --> 00:01:46,599
(Grandmother.)

43
00:01:47,120 --> 00:01:47,919
(Father.)

44
00:01:48,760 --> 00:01:49,559
(Mother.)

45
00:01:49,879 --> 00:01:52,760
(Auntie. Thank you for helping me
reunite with Xiaoyao.)

46
00:01:52,919 --> 00:01:53,639
(This time,)

47
00:01:54,120 --> 00:01:56,120
(I'll protect
my little sister for sure.)

48
00:01:57,178 --> 00:01:58,760
(Yiqing Garden)

49
00:01:58,760 --> 00:02:00,680
I told Queen Mother
about you in the letter.

50
00:02:00,680 --> 00:02:01,599
She agreed

51
00:02:02,319 --> 00:02:03,480
to restore your look.

52
00:02:04,639 --> 00:02:05,440
Great.

53
00:02:05,919 --> 00:02:07,279
I'll go with her.

54
00:02:09,839 --> 00:02:10,720
What a nice song.

55
00:02:10,800 --> 00:02:11,919
If you want,

56
00:02:12,080 --> 00:02:13,240
I'll make him play

57
00:02:13,240 --> 00:02:14,039
for you.

58
00:02:17,479 --> 00:02:18,639
Who's playing the flute?

59
00:02:18,919 --> 00:02:21,039
It matches your zither so well.

60
00:02:22,279 --> 00:02:24,520
The zither matched your flute perfectly.

61
00:02:24,720 --> 00:02:26,320
I wonder if it's a woman playing.

62
00:02:26,880 --> 00:02:28,919
The woman in the red gown

63
00:02:29,160 --> 00:02:30,240
is Fangfeng Yiying.

64
00:02:30,639 --> 00:02:31,600
It's her?

65
00:02:44,039 --> 00:02:44,559
Go now.

66
00:02:45,376 --> 00:02:45,952
Go.

67
00:02:52,720 --> 00:02:53,360
Be careful.

68
00:02:55,320 --> 00:02:55,960
Look after Nian.

69
00:02:56,096 --> 00:02:56,600
Okay.

70
00:02:56,896 --> 00:02:57,440
Let's go.

71
00:03:19,559 --> 00:03:21,039
Fortunately, it was only
a shoulder wound.

72
00:03:21,360 --> 00:03:22,440
It didn't hit any vital parts.

73
00:03:22,839 --> 00:03:23,839
Do you think

74
00:03:24,000 --> 00:03:25,839
this bamboo flute is his?

75
00:03:25,919 --> 00:03:27,639
We can ask when he wakes up.

76
00:03:27,960 --> 00:03:29,679
I hope we didn't save the wrong person.

77
00:03:33,279 --> 00:03:33,960
You're awake.

78
00:03:34,320 --> 00:03:35,119
Where am I?

79
00:03:35,199 --> 00:03:35,919
Don't get up,

80
00:03:35,919 --> 00:03:37,000
or you may tear your wound.

81
00:03:37,000 --> 00:03:38,199
This is the Chenrong Mansion.

82
00:03:39,440 --> 00:03:40,720
May I ask if Chenrong Yi is...?

83
00:03:40,800 --> 00:03:42,279
Chenrong Yi is my father.

84
00:03:42,360 --> 00:03:43,639
My name is Chenrong Xinyue.

85
00:03:43,720 --> 00:03:44,800
Thank you, Miss Chenrong.

86
00:03:44,839 --> 00:03:46,039
Is this yours?

87
00:03:46,119 --> 00:03:47,440
Yes, this is mine.

88
00:03:47,520 --> 00:03:49,759
Is it you who was playing the flute

89
00:03:49,800 --> 00:03:50,520
on the lake?

90
00:03:50,520 --> 00:03:51,639
It was me.

91
00:03:52,039 --> 00:03:53,320
Could it be that you were the one

92
00:03:53,880 --> 00:03:55,000
who played the guqin?

93
00:03:56,360 --> 00:03:57,119
I'm Xuan,

94
00:03:57,679 --> 00:03:59,000
from Haoling's Dragon Squad.

95
00:03:59,039 --> 00:04:00,559
I'll leave now.

96
00:04:00,720 --> 00:04:02,440
You should stay here to recover.

97
00:04:02,440 --> 00:04:04,039
If you don't want your family worried,

98
00:04:04,039 --> 00:04:06,679
I'll have someone
deliver a message for you.

99
00:04:06,759 --> 00:04:08,119
Thank you.

100
00:04:10,679 --> 00:04:12,720
Thank you, sir,
for agreeing to play with me.

101
00:04:12,919 --> 00:04:14,279
Miss Chenrong, you're too polite.

102
00:04:14,960 --> 00:04:16,440
Compared to your favor
of saving my life,

103
00:04:16,480 --> 00:04:18,559
playing a song is just small-fry.

104
00:04:19,200 --> 00:04:21,440
The flowers in the garden
are in full bloom today.

105
00:04:21,440 --> 00:04:23,320
I'll take you around.

106
00:04:23,399 --> 00:04:24,839
It's time for me to take my medicine.

107
00:04:25,320 --> 00:04:27,119
I need to go back to my room now.

108
00:04:27,559 --> 00:04:28,519
Then next time.

109
00:04:30,920 --> 00:04:32,920
Alright, my wound doesn't hurt anymore.

110
00:04:33,480 --> 00:04:34,279
Don't be angry with me.

111
00:04:34,519 --> 00:04:36,279
Unless life is threatened,

112
00:04:36,279 --> 00:04:37,040
no one likes

113
00:04:37,040 --> 00:04:39,839
to act by hurting themselves.

114
00:04:39,839 --> 00:04:41,519
I had someone investigate
Fangfeng Yiying

115
00:04:41,839 --> 00:04:43,760
after the last time I got hurt.

116
00:04:43,920 --> 00:04:45,359
She was probably instructed by someone

117
00:04:45,559 --> 00:04:46,799
to assassinate me.

118
00:04:46,920 --> 00:04:48,480
Could it be someone from Xiyan?

119
00:04:48,480 --> 00:04:50,920
This matter is most likely
related to my uncle.

120
00:04:51,040 --> 00:04:54,760
It seems that the Fangfeng Family
has likely sided with him.

121
00:04:55,000 --> 00:04:57,079
If it hadn't been for me
wanting to hear her play the guqin,

122
00:04:57,079 --> 00:04:59,320
you wouldn't have
had the chance to play the flute,

123
00:05:00,119 --> 00:05:01,839
and Chenrong Xinyue
wouldn't have developed

124
00:05:02,200 --> 00:05:03,640
a liking for you.

125
00:05:04,600 --> 00:05:06,440
If I hadn't played the flute for you,

126
00:05:06,440 --> 00:05:08,000
I wouldn't have lured their boat over.

127
00:05:08,000 --> 00:05:09,119
If I hadn't lured them over,

128
00:05:09,119 --> 00:05:10,320
I wouldn't have encountered them

129
00:05:10,320 --> 00:05:12,160
and wouldn't have had
all these troubles.

130
00:05:12,160 --> 00:05:14,079
I was the victim
of your unintended harm.

131
00:05:14,079 --> 00:05:15,920
If you hadn't met Chenrong Xinyue,

132
00:05:16,320 --> 00:05:19,600
how would you have met people
from the Chishui and Chenrong Families?

133
00:05:19,679 --> 00:05:21,119
I should thank you?

134
00:05:23,679 --> 00:05:25,640
The Chenrong and Chishui Families

135
00:05:25,640 --> 00:05:27,880
were clans you wanted
to get acquainted with and win over.

136
00:05:27,880 --> 00:05:29,600
I didn't expect such a chance,

137
00:05:29,600 --> 00:05:31,720
and we actually met Chenrong Xinyue.

138
00:05:31,760 --> 00:05:33,399
Whether the Chenrong
and Chishui Families

139
00:05:33,399 --> 00:05:35,160
will stand on our side or out

140
00:05:35,279 --> 00:05:37,359
doesn't depend on

141
00:05:37,359 --> 00:05:38,720
Chenrong Xinyue's trivial liking for me,

142
00:05:38,880 --> 00:05:41,200
but on the benefits
I can bring them in the future.

143
00:05:41,200 --> 00:05:42,040
You are

144
00:05:43,040 --> 00:05:45,320
too clear-headed, too rational.

145
00:05:47,760 --> 00:05:49,440
Fenglong, let me introduce you.

146
00:05:49,440 --> 00:05:51,359
This is Xuan
from the Dragon Squad of Haoling.

147
00:05:51,359 --> 00:05:52,200
Nice to see you.

148
00:05:52,200 --> 00:05:55,040
Nice to meet you,
Mr. Chishui and Miss Chenrong.

149
00:05:55,079 --> 00:05:56,239
So the friend of Jing

150
00:05:56,239 --> 00:05:57,200
is you.

151
00:05:57,200 --> 00:05:58,079
You know each other?

152
00:05:59,239 --> 00:06:00,880
I heard that a court official of Xiyan

153
00:06:00,880 --> 00:06:02,320
impeached Mr. Chenrong.

154
00:06:02,359 --> 00:06:04,320
Yes, father has been
worried about this matter recently.

155
00:06:04,320 --> 00:06:08,079
If one must say
that Mr. Chenrong is colluding

156
00:06:08,119 --> 00:06:09,600
with the Chenrong rebels,

157
00:06:09,600 --> 00:06:10,880
there's nothing wrong with that.

158
00:06:10,959 --> 00:06:11,920
Hundreds of years ago,

159
00:06:11,920 --> 00:06:14,239
when Mr. Chenrong took over
the Central Plains, he said

160
00:06:14,239 --> 00:06:15,440
his loyalty goes to common people,

161
00:06:15,720 --> 00:06:17,119
and his pursuit is peace

162
00:06:17,119 --> 00:06:18,799
and well-being all over the world.

163
00:06:19,279 --> 00:06:21,320
He never said
he would be loyal to a single man.

164
00:06:21,320 --> 00:06:23,079
What he has been striving for is great.

165
00:06:23,119 --> 00:06:24,920
Isn't the peaceful life
of Central Plains' civilians

166
00:06:24,959 --> 00:06:27,679
important?

167
00:06:27,920 --> 00:06:29,799
After Mr. Chenrong
took over Central Plains,

168
00:06:30,279 --> 00:06:32,079
with private negotiations,

169
00:06:32,760 --> 00:06:34,880
many betrayers surrendered,

170
00:06:34,920 --> 00:06:36,679
which stopped many wars.

171
00:06:36,799 --> 00:06:38,920
If it weren't
for Mr. Chenrong's collusion,

172
00:06:39,040 --> 00:06:40,519
as Central Plains enjoyed many people,

173
00:06:40,720 --> 00:06:42,480
there wouldn't be

174
00:06:42,720 --> 00:06:45,119
just tens of thousands
of betrayers left,

175
00:06:45,440 --> 00:06:46,920
hiding in Qingshui.

176
00:06:47,000 --> 00:06:47,760
Well done.

177
00:06:47,839 --> 00:06:48,880
I toast you.

178
00:06:49,760 --> 00:06:51,359
Miss Chenrong

179
00:06:51,359 --> 00:06:53,239
was quite interested in you.

180
00:06:53,320 --> 00:06:54,679
She looks serious

181
00:06:55,359 --> 00:06:57,839
because I am Xiyan Cang Xuan.

182
00:06:58,079 --> 00:06:59,399
But I'm not in a position to judge her.

183
00:06:59,399 --> 00:07:01,040
I don't refuse her

184
00:07:01,079 --> 00:07:02,920
just because

185
00:07:02,920 --> 00:07:04,720
she is Chenrong Xinyue.

186
00:07:05,040 --> 00:07:06,480
I can't offend enemies,

187
00:07:06,720 --> 00:07:07,600
nor

188
00:07:08,440 --> 00:07:09,559
get close to someone I like.

189
00:07:09,839 --> 00:07:10,480
But this is

190
00:07:10,480 --> 00:07:12,160
the price I need to pay

191
00:07:12,160 --> 00:07:14,040
to return to Xiyan Mountain.

192
00:07:14,239 --> 00:07:15,200
It must be a bloody path

193
00:07:15,720 --> 00:07:17,679
returning to Xiyan Mountain.

194
00:07:17,839 --> 00:07:19,359
I must stand on Zhaoyun Peak

195
00:07:20,839 --> 00:07:22,440
on my auntie's
anniversary death next year.

196
00:07:22,799 --> 00:07:23,600
Cang Xuan.

197
00:07:24,480 --> 00:07:25,239
Let's

198
00:07:25,519 --> 00:07:26,559
go home together.

199
00:07:27,519 --> 00:07:28,040
Okay.

200
00:07:28,679 --> 00:07:29,880
Let's go home together.

201
00:07:38,040 --> 00:07:38,760
Mother.

202
00:07:38,760 --> 00:07:40,200
- Auntie.
- Look.

203
00:07:40,399 --> 00:07:42,000
Look, I picked
these Poinciana flowers today.

204
00:07:42,200 --> 00:07:42,959
Have a smell.

205
00:07:43,600 --> 00:07:44,519
They smell so good.

206
00:07:46,239 --> 00:07:47,480
I have kept you waiting so long.

207
00:07:47,559 --> 00:07:49,160
What is your purpose of coming back?

208
00:07:49,320 --> 00:07:50,640
I want the Xiyan Mountain.

209
00:07:51,839 --> 00:07:52,839
And there's another reason

210
00:07:53,160 --> 00:07:54,839
you might not believe.

211
00:07:55,040 --> 00:07:56,279
I missed you.

212
00:07:57,760 --> 00:08:00,279
Your two royal uncles and a few brothers

213
00:08:00,279 --> 00:08:02,079
all want the Xiyan Mountain.

214
00:08:02,079 --> 00:08:03,119
If you want it,

215
00:08:03,119 --> 00:08:04,559
find your own way.

216
00:08:04,600 --> 00:08:05,839
I won't help you.

217
00:08:06,160 --> 00:08:07,000
I understand.

218
00:08:07,880 --> 00:08:09,880
Isn't it just like the swing
from our childhood?

219
00:08:09,959 --> 00:08:12,040
Did you really come back
for our grandfather?

220
00:08:12,224 --> 00:08:12,760
Yes.

221
00:08:12,839 --> 00:08:14,600
He is not only our grandfather,

222
00:08:14,600 --> 00:08:15,760
but also a king.

223
00:08:16,079 --> 00:08:18,600
To become the master
of the Xiyan Mountain,

224
00:08:18,600 --> 00:08:20,519
do you have to be like our grandfather?

225
00:08:20,799 --> 00:08:22,880
Being strong and cold.

226
00:08:23,079 --> 00:08:25,559
I'm not qualified to answer it yet.

227
00:08:25,720 --> 00:08:27,119
Because I'm not yet.

228
00:08:27,160 --> 00:08:28,279
There's still too little

229
00:08:28,440 --> 00:08:29,920
I can do for you.

230
00:08:30,600 --> 00:08:31,200
Xiaoyao.

231
00:08:31,519 --> 00:08:33,520
You just need to stand by my side,

232
00:08:33,640 --> 00:08:34,799
and that's enough.

233
00:08:56,679 --> 00:08:57,880
This time, I came to see you

234
00:08:57,880 --> 00:08:58,799
for important matters.

235
00:08:59,039 --> 00:09:00,840
There is no need
for formality between us.

236
00:09:00,840 --> 00:09:02,719
Since you chose to return to Xiyan Town,

237
00:09:02,760 --> 00:09:04,719
I suppose you are determined
to claim that throne.

238
00:09:04,719 --> 00:09:06,400
But you left Xiyan Town
when you were young,

239
00:09:06,400 --> 00:09:08,320
and your uncles have been
ruling for over 1,000 years.

240
00:09:08,320 --> 00:09:09,320
I'm not looking down on you,

241
00:09:09,320 --> 00:09:11,119
but what do you have
to compete with them?

242
00:09:11,119 --> 00:09:12,599
I do have the ambition,

243
00:09:13,280 --> 00:09:15,559
and it's true
that I'm struggling in Xiyan Town.

244
00:09:15,799 --> 00:09:17,799
You could say I'm barely surviving.

245
00:09:17,960 --> 00:09:19,640
If you have any suggestions,

246
00:09:19,760 --> 00:09:20,760
feel free to speak.

247
00:09:20,960 --> 00:09:23,119
All of this now belong to Xiyan.

248
00:09:23,119 --> 00:09:24,000
Cang Xuan.

249
00:09:24,320 --> 00:09:25,400
Give up Xiyan Town

250
00:09:25,599 --> 00:09:26,559
and come to Central Plains.

251
00:09:26,719 --> 00:09:28,679
The center of the entire Dahuang
is Central Plains.

252
00:09:28,799 --> 00:09:29,880
One day,

253
00:09:30,200 --> 00:09:31,599
if you want to march south,

254
00:09:31,599 --> 00:09:32,760
it will also be easy.

255
00:09:34,440 --> 00:09:35,679
A word from you

256
00:09:35,679 --> 00:09:37,159
woke me up.

257
00:09:37,559 --> 00:09:38,400
I will never

258
00:09:38,919 --> 00:09:40,200
forget this favor.

259
00:09:51,400 --> 00:09:52,880
Xiaoyao kept chatting with me

260
00:09:53,280 --> 00:09:54,080
and lost track of time.

261
00:09:54,599 --> 00:09:56,280
If you fail her and break her heart

262
00:09:56,280 --> 00:09:57,359
in the future,

263
00:09:57,479 --> 00:09:59,440
I will definitely take your life.

264
00:09:59,559 --> 00:10:00,719
If that day really comes,

265
00:10:00,840 --> 00:10:01,960
kill me.

266
00:10:14,520 --> 00:10:15,880
What's so good about this map?

267
00:10:16,400 --> 00:10:19,000
It was extremely difficult

268
00:10:19,000 --> 00:10:20,280
to come to Xiyan Town,

269
00:10:20,679 --> 00:10:22,640
and now, it's also extremely difficult

270
00:10:22,919 --> 00:10:24,239
to leave here.

271
00:10:27,400 --> 00:10:28,799
Destroying

272
00:10:28,799 --> 00:10:29,919
yourself

273
00:10:29,919 --> 00:10:30,919
or abandoning

274
00:10:30,919 --> 00:10:32,000
yourself,

275
00:10:32,080 --> 00:10:33,159
which one would you choose?

276
00:10:37,559 --> 00:10:39,200
This pill is called Free and Easy.

277
00:10:39,280 --> 00:10:40,320
With just one pill,

278
