was made from Kunwood,

559
00:22:43,079 --> 00:22:44,000
which was solid.

560
00:22:44,079 --> 00:22:45,359
How did it break?

561
00:22:45,359 --> 00:22:46,160
I found white ants

562
00:22:46,400 --> 00:22:48,239
under the broken bucket arch.

563
00:22:48,239 --> 00:22:49,479
I thought they were common ants.

564
00:22:49,479 --> 00:22:50,400
But the experts said that

565
00:22:50,400 --> 00:22:51,160
those ants were bred

566
00:22:51,239 --> 00:22:53,959
by chalcedony from Mount Jade

567
00:22:54,119 --> 00:22:55,119
and could eat Kunwood.

568
00:22:55,119 --> 00:22:57,119
Someone must have placed them there.

569
00:22:57,119 --> 00:22:59,239
Your Lordship. I went to arrest
the carpenter Peng Shan.

570
00:22:59,239 --> 00:23:01,079
But he had committed suicide at home.

571
00:23:01,239 --> 00:23:03,000
We lost our key witness.

572
00:23:04,599 --> 00:23:06,599
You are drafting the restoration plan
for Daming Palace?

573
00:23:07,719 --> 00:23:09,359
Grandfather hasn't issued
the imperial order,

574
00:23:09,359 --> 00:23:12,239
but Daming Palace
still collapsed under my watch.

575
00:23:12,359 --> 00:23:13,599
I need to do what I should.

576
00:23:13,760 --> 00:23:15,719
Even if there's no evidence
of embezzlement,

577
00:23:15,760 --> 00:23:18,400
Yue Liang probably
won't let it go easily.

578
00:23:18,400 --> 00:23:20,119
I have never cut corners,

579
00:23:20,719 --> 00:23:23,040
so I'm not afraid that he'll find out
any evidence of my embezzlement.

580
00:23:23,239 --> 00:23:25,199
But I worry he would follow the clues

581
00:23:25,199 --> 00:23:26,520
and find out other things.

582
00:23:29,599 --> 00:23:30,239
Xuan.

583
00:23:30,400 --> 00:23:31,680
I want to go to the Xiyan Mountain

584
00:23:31,959 --> 00:23:32,959
to see my grandfather.

585
00:23:33,079 --> 00:23:35,040
Are you going to plead
with him for my sake?

586
00:23:35,479 --> 00:23:36,760
That's partly true.

587
00:23:36,760 --> 00:23:38,119
I'll go see Grandfather

588
00:23:38,119 --> 00:23:39,439
and say a few words by the way.

589
00:23:39,599 --> 00:23:42,239
We can't let your uncles say everything,

590
00:23:42,239 --> 00:23:44,199
and we don't even
have a chance to rebut.

591
00:23:44,280 --> 00:23:45,719
I have something to say to you.

592
00:23:47,920 --> 00:23:48,959
I'm going to get married.

593
00:23:48,959 --> 00:23:50,479
I've already written to Grandfather,

594
00:23:50,479 --> 00:23:51,760
asking for his approval.

595
00:23:53,760 --> 00:23:55,520
Are you marrying Chenrong Xinyue?

596
00:23:55,520 --> 00:23:56,199
No.

597
00:23:56,199 --> 00:23:57,000
No?

598
00:23:57,040 --> 00:23:58,479
I'm marrying Shen Shuhui.

599
00:23:58,479 --> 00:24:00,880
Her family's the strongest
of the six major families.

600
00:24:00,920 --> 00:24:03,040
Even the Chenrong royal family
had to marry them in the past.

601
00:24:03,119 --> 00:24:05,040
The chief of the Shen family
has a good impression of me,

602
00:24:05,640 --> 00:24:07,959
so he's willing
to take a risk to support me.

603
00:24:10,400 --> 00:24:12,160
I don't care what method you use

604
00:24:12,160 --> 00:24:13,680
or what you want to do.

605
00:24:13,880 --> 00:24:15,680
I just want you to live well.

606
00:24:16,640 --> 00:24:17,400
I've told you

607
00:24:18,760 --> 00:24:20,119
I'd make Poinciana flowers bloom

608
00:24:20,599 --> 00:24:21,920
all over the Chenrong Mountain.

609
00:24:23,319 --> 00:24:25,439
Xiyan Cang Xuan,
please accept the decree.

610
00:24:25,680 --> 00:24:28,439
Xiyan Cang Xuan was careless

611
00:24:28,640 --> 00:24:29,880
and neglected supervision,

612
00:24:30,079 --> 00:24:32,199
leading to the collapse
of the Daming Hall.

613
00:24:32,239 --> 00:24:34,839
He should have been dismissed
for negligence.

614
00:24:34,959 --> 00:24:37,400
Considering his sincere repentance,

615
00:24:37,880 --> 00:24:39,920
he is specially allowed
to atone for his mistake

616
00:24:40,079 --> 00:24:41,520
by rebuilding the Daming Hall.

617
00:24:41,599 --> 00:24:42,920
Shen Shuhui from the Shen family

618
00:24:42,920 --> 00:24:44,160
is gentle, kind

619
00:24:44,319 --> 00:24:45,560
and beautiful.

620
00:24:46,000 --> 00:24:49,920
She is specially granted to the prince,
Xiyan Cang Xuan, as a secondary wife.

621
00:24:49,920 --> 00:24:50,839
Thank you, Your Majesty.

622
00:24:52,416 --> 00:24:56,608
♪Looking up, I saw you♪

623
00:24:57,359 --> 00:24:58,599
Put down the fan.

624
00:25:01,088 --> 00:25:05,120
♪You appear in the snow♪

625
00:25:05,439 --> 00:25:06,479
(Do not congratulate me.)

626
00:25:09,760 --> 00:25:11,760
♪You appear as the smoke rises♪

627
00:25:11,760 --> 00:25:12,959
The magpie brings good news,

628
00:25:13,280 --> 00:25:14,640
and flowers bloom together.

629
00:25:14,839 --> 00:25:16,040
May you two be filled with love,

630
00:25:16,199 --> 00:25:17,760
and may you be blessed
with many children.

631
00:25:17,800 --> 00:25:18,920
Congratulations.

632
00:25:19,920 --> 00:25:21,599
Congratulations.

633
00:25:21,599 --> 00:25:23,560
(We'll never be apart from each other.)

634
00:25:23,680 --> 00:25:24,599
(Deal.)

635
00:25:27,119 --> 00:25:28,479
His Majesty was attacked.

636
00:25:28,640 --> 00:25:29,599
You are summoned

637
00:25:29,920 --> 00:25:31,920
to the Zezhou residence.

638
00:25:32,199 --> 00:25:32,880
Is Grandfather fine?

639
00:25:33,160 --> 00:25:34,239
It was a narrow escape.

640
00:25:34,520 --> 00:25:35,599
Sorry to disappoint you.

641
00:25:35,839 --> 00:25:36,719
How can you say so?

642
00:25:37,000 --> 00:25:37,680
Something's fishy.

643
00:25:37,760 --> 00:25:38,640
Your Highness can't go.

644
00:25:38,640 --> 00:25:39,920
If you go,

645
00:25:39,920 --> 00:25:41,839
you leave your fate to His Majesty.

646
00:25:41,959 --> 00:25:43,479
Even if he lets you go,

647
00:25:43,479 --> 00:25:44,920
Fifth King will try to kill you.

648
00:25:45,040 --> 00:25:46,160
I have to go.

649
00:25:46,160 --> 00:25:47,479
If I don't go,

650
00:25:47,640 --> 00:25:48,640
my uncle can frame me

651
00:25:48,640 --> 00:25:49,520
for planning a coup.

652
00:25:49,599 --> 00:25:51,640
All my followers will be executed.

653
00:25:52,000 --> 00:25:53,479
I don't want to die like that.

654
00:25:54,839 --> 00:25:57,040
Neither do I want you talented people

655
00:25:58,000 --> 00:25:59,079
to die like that.

656
00:26:00,520 --> 00:26:02,400
Cang Xuan has been industrious.

657
00:26:02,439 --> 00:26:05,359
You made all the clans
so grateful to you.

658
00:26:05,359 --> 00:26:06,959
But you married Miss Shen

659
00:26:07,000 --> 00:26:09,119
and truly hurt our feelings.

660
00:26:10,079 --> 00:26:11,079
Your Highness,

661
00:26:11,239 --> 00:26:13,119
you probably forgot all about

662
00:26:13,199 --> 00:26:14,560
our old clans of Xiyan.

663
00:26:14,760 --> 00:26:16,479
As the Prince of Xiyan,

664
00:26:16,520 --> 00:26:19,800
I only married Miss Shen
to promote harmony with the clans.

665
00:26:20,000 --> 00:26:23,280
One can only be their king
once he sees those clansmen

666
00:26:23,920 --> 00:26:25,800
as his own citizens.

667
00:26:26,199 --> 00:26:27,920
What are citizens?

668
00:26:28,160 --> 00:26:29,880
What is a king?

669
00:26:29,959 --> 00:26:31,000
In the beginning,

670
00:26:31,400 --> 00:26:32,880
Dahuang was a united territory.

671
00:26:32,880 --> 00:26:35,920
If Pangu, Fuxi,
or Nuwa comes back to life,

672
00:26:36,096 --> 00:26:37,920
they'll see the Xiyan clan
and Chenrong clan

673
00:26:37,920 --> 00:26:40,680
as their own citizens.

674
00:26:41,000 --> 00:26:43,079
The Xiyan family
already rules the Central Plains.

675
00:26:43,400 --> 00:26:46,400
How is Zhiyi different from Xiyan Town?

676
00:26:46,599 --> 00:26:48,479
How dare you.

677
00:26:49,959 --> 00:26:54,119
Were you only building the palace
on Chenrong Mountain?

678
00:26:54,319 --> 00:26:56,000
I remember your teaching

679
00:26:56,400 --> 00:26:59,719
and only do
what the Prince of Xiyan should do.

680
00:27:05,504 --> 00:27:07,560
My spirit power is limited.
I can only afford three shots.

681
00:27:07,560 --> 00:27:08,359
That's enough.

682
00:27:27,479 --> 00:27:29,479
Assassins!

683
00:27:30,880 --> 00:27:33,119
The ceremony begins.

684
00:27:33,319 --> 00:27:35,560
First bow to the heaven.

685
00:27:36,800 --> 00:27:39,040
Second bow to the earth.

686
00:27:40,160 --> 00:27:43,239
Third bow to the mountains of Chenrong.

687
00:27:43,599 --> 00:27:45,719
Finished.

688
00:27:45,800 --> 00:27:49,199
I won't announce the Crown Prince,

689
00:27:49,319 --> 00:27:53,959
but who becomes
the king of Xiyan Kingdom.

690
00:27:54,599 --> 00:27:58,640
This king should have a great ambition,

691
00:27:58,800 --> 00:28:00,359
a keen mind,

692
00:28:00,359 --> 00:28:01,920
a broad heart,

693
00:28:01,920 --> 00:28:03,959
and vigorous energy.

694
00:28:04,160 --> 00:28:04,959
Deyan.

695
00:28:05,439 --> 00:28:05,959
Father.

696
00:28:06,079 --> 00:28:07,640
You did a good job.

697
00:28:07,920 --> 00:28:08,719
Thank you, Father.

698
00:28:08,719 --> 00:28:12,680
You arranged a good ceremony.

699
00:28:12,719 --> 00:28:14,520
The new king ascends,

700
00:28:14,520 --> 00:28:16,439
demonstrating his power.

701
00:28:16,719 --> 00:28:17,560
Cang Xuan.

702
00:28:18,119 --> 00:28:19,119
Come here.

703
00:28:40,359 --> 00:28:41,640
From today,

704
00:28:41,719 --> 00:28:45,680
Xiyan Cang Xuan is the king
of Xiyan Kingdom.

705
00:28:48,719 --> 00:28:50,839
Greetings, Your Majesty.

706
00:28:51,079 --> 00:28:53,439
Greetings, Your Majesty.
